1892:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @brief  Configure the TIM commutation event sequence.
1893:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @note  This function is mandatory to use the commutation event in order to
1894:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        update the configuration at each commutation detection on the TRGI input of the Timer,
1895:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        the typical use of this feature is with the use of another Timer(interface Timer)
1896:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        configured in Hall sensor interface, this interface Timer will generate the
1897:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        commutation at its TRGO output (connected to Timer used in this function) each time
1898:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        the TI1 of the Interface Timer detect a commutation at its input TI1.
1899:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @param  htim TIM handle
1900:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @param  InputTrigger the Internal trigger corresponding to the Timer Interfacing with the Hall 
1901:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
1902:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR0: Internal trigger 0 selected
1903:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR1: Internal trigger 1 selected
1904:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR2: Internal trigger 2 selected
1905:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR3: Internal trigger 3 selected
1906:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR4: Internal trigger 4 selected
1907:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR5: Internal trigger 5 selected
1908:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR6: Internal trigger 6 selected
1909:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR7: Internal trigger 7 selected
1910:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR8: Internal trigger 8 selected
